    <br>
    (iii)	140 000 000 = 140 x 1 000 000 =><strong> 140 million or 0.14 billion</strong>
    <br>
    (iv)	300 000 000 000 = 300 x 1 000 000 000 => <strong>300 billion or 0.3 trillion</strong>
    
    </div>
